metadata.description:
At this time, the middle-aged man stepped on Lu Ming's back, a sharp knife appeared in his hand, and called: "Lu Ming, give your blood!"



Ah!



Spine, the pain of the heart suddenly submerged Lu Ming, Lu Ming hoarseness roar, the voice is full of loneliness and despair.



Gradually, Lu Ming was immersed in the boundless darkness.



"Lu Yao, I treat you like love, why do you hurt me!"
